<h2>Cambridge Energy Incentives</h2>
<p>Cambridge residents have access to several attractive incentives for solar and HVAC upgrades. The federal solar Investment Tax Credit (ITC) provides a 30% credit on solar installation costs through 2032, then stepping down to 26% in 2033 and 22% in 2034. Massachusetts offers additional state incentives through the Solar Massachusetts Renewable Target (SMART) program, which provides performance-based incentives for solar production over 10-20 years, adding significant value to solar investments.</p>

