<p>Eversource's Green Communities initiative provides additional support for HVAC efficiency upgrades, including rebates for smart thermostats, high-efficiency heat pumps, and whole-home energy management systems. Cambridge residents should coordinate solar installations with any planned electrical service upgrades, as older homes may need panel upgrades to accommodate both solar inverters and high-efficiency electric heating systems.</p>

